                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At their meeting on September 13, the Foreign Ministers of the United States, the
                    United Kingdom and France, discussed the question of access to Berlin and the
                    interzonal trade agreement. For a record of their discussion, see Tripartite
                    Min–5, <ref target="frus1951v03p1#pg_1279">page 1279</ref>.</p>
            </div>
